<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbcfe9734-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c" identifier="/us/usc/t13/s13"><num value="13">§ 13.</num><heading> Procurement of professional services</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall have authority to contract with educational and other research organizations for the preparation of monographs and other reports and materials of a similar nature.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbcfe9735-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/85/207/s5">Pub. L. 85–207, § 5</ref>, <date date="1957-08-28">Aug. 28, 1957</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/71/481">71 Stat. 481</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
